"It’s an exciting time to be joining Network Rail High Speed. We are making the biggest fundamental change to our business in its history, as we look to modernise and deliver an even more sustainable and high performing high-speed railway than we already have today!As a Shift Station Manager, you’ll be managing the day to day performance of the station team within set resources, budgets and objectives. Providing consistent and excellent customer service is at the heart of what our Shift Station Managers do while also providing an operationally safe and secure station environment for all our stakeholders, such as TOCs, passengers and retailers.We’re now recruiting for roles at St Pancras International, Stratford International and Ebbsfleet International. However, occasional travel to our other offices and site locations along the high-speed line and across the network is/may be expected."